<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>{% block title %}Planorama{% endblock %}</title>
    <link rel="icon" href="{{ asset('img/logo.png') }}">

    <style>
        /* RESET */
        body, html {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: 'EB Garamond', serif;
            
            font-size: 1.2rem;
        }

        /* HEADER GLOBAL */
        .main-header {
            top: 20px;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            z-index: 1000;
            background-color: #dcd6d0;
        }

        .header-container {
            width: 90%;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
        }

        /* LOGO */
        .logo-nav {
            height: 40px;
        }

        /* MENU CENTRAL */
        .header-center {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.4);
            backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
            padding: 12px 40px;
            border-radius: 40px;
            display: flex;
            gap: 25px;
        }

        .header-center a {
            text-decoration: none;
            color: #7d6b5d;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            transition: 0.3s;
        }

        .header-center a:hover,
        .header-center a.active {
            background-color: #8b735b;
            color: white;
        }

        /* BOUTONS */
        .btn-nav {
            text-decoration: none;
            font-family: inter;
            padding: 10px 25px;
            border-radius: 25px;
            font-weight : regular;
            font-size: 20px;
            transition: 0.3s;
        }

        .btn-primary-nav {
            background-color: #8b735b;
            color: white !important;
            border: 2px solid #8b735b;
        }


        .btn-outline-nav {
            background-color: transparent;
            color: white !important;
            border: 0.2rem solid white;
        }

        .btn-outline-nav:hover {
            background-color: #8b735b;
            color: white !important;
            border: 0.2rem solid #8b735b;
        }

        .user-email {
            color: #7d6b5d;
            font-style: italic;
            margin-right: 10px;
            font-size: 20px;
        }

        /* FOOTER */

        .main-footer {
        padding: 20px;
        background-color: #fcfaf8;
        }

        .footer-container {
            background-color: #dcd6d0; /* un peu plus foncé */
            border-top-left-radius: 100px;
            border-top-right-radius: 100px;
            padding: 60px 10%;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: flex-start;
        }

        /* GAUCHE */
        .footer-left {
            flex: 1;
        }

        .footer-left h2 {
            color: #7d6b5d;
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .footer-left p {
            color: #8b735b;
            max-width: 400px;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }

        .newsletter-form {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 10px;
            max-width: 300px;
        }

        .newsletter-form input {
            padding: 12px 20px;
            border-radius: 25px;
            border: 1px solid #d1ccc7;
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.3);
            outline: none;
        }

        .newsletter-form button {
            padding: 12px;
            border-radius: 25px;
            border: none;
            background-color: #8b735b;
            color: white;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .social-icons {
            display: flex;
            gap: 20px;
            margin-top: 30px;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
        }

        .social-icons a {
            color: #7d6b5d;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        /* DROITE */
        .footer-right {
            flex: 1;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: flex-end;
        }

        .footer-logo {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }

        .footer-logo img {
            width: 100px; 
            display: block;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .footer-logo span {
            color: #7d6b5d;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 1.7rem; 
        }

        .footer-links {
            display: flex;
            gap: 50px;
        }

        .link-column {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 12px;
        }

        .link-column a {
            text-decoration: none;
            color: #7d6b5d;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            transition: 0.3s;
        }

        .link-column a:hover {
            color: #8b735b;
            padding-left: 5px;
        }

        @media (max-width: 900px) {
            .footer-container {
                flex-direction: column;
                border-radius: 50px;
                gap: 50px;
            }

            .footer-right {
                align-items: flex-start;
            }
        }
    </style>

    {% block stylesheets %}{% endblock %}
    {% block javascripts %}{{ importmap('app') }}{% endblock %}
    {% block importmap %}{{ importmap('app') }}{% endblock %}
</head>

<body>

{% block navigation %}
<header class="main-header">
    <div class="header-container">

        <!-- GAUCHE -->
        <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 20px;">
            <div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center;">
                <a href="{{ path('app_home') }}">
                    <img src="{{ asset('img/logo_fond_marron.png') }}" class="logo-nav" alt="Planorama">
                </a>
                <span style="font-size: 1.3rem; color: #7d6b5d;">Planorama</span>
            </div>

            {% if app.user %}
                <span class="user-email">
                    Bonjour, {{ app.user.pseudo|default(app.user.email) }}
                </span>
            {% endif %}
        </div>

        <!-- MENU -->
        <div class="header-center">
            <a href="{{ path('app_home') }}">Accueil</a>
            <a href="{{ path('app_plan_index') }}">Mes projets</a>
            <a href="{{ path('app_item_catalog_index') }}">Inspiration</a>
        </div>

        <!-- DROITE -->
        <div>
            {% if app.user %}
                <a href="{{ path('app_logout') }}" class="btn-nav btn-outline-nav">Déconnexion</a>
            {% else %}
                <a href="{{ path('app_login') }}" class="btn-nav btn-primary-nav">Connexion</a>
                <a href="{{ path('app_register') }}" class="btn-nav btn-outline-nav">Inscription</a>
            {% endif %}
        </div>

    </div>
</header>
{% endblock %}

<main>
    {% block body %}{% endblock %}
</main>

<footer class="main-footer">
    <div class="footer-container">

        <div class="footer-left">
            <h2>Prêt à transformer<br>votre intérieur ?</h2>
            <p>Rejoignez des milliers de passionnés de design et commencez votre projet gratuitement dès aujourd'hui.</p>

            <form class="newsletter-form">
                <input type="email" placeholder="Email">
                <button type="submit">S'inscrire à la newsletter</button>
            </form>

            <div class="social-icons">
                <a href="#"><i class="fab fa-instagram"></i></a>
                <a href="#"><i class="fab fa-facebook-f"></i></a>
                <a href="#"><i class="fab fa-youtube"></i></a>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="footer-right">
            <div class="footer-logo">
                <img src="{{ asset('img/logo_marron.png') }}" alt="Logo">
                <span>Planorama</span>
            </div>

            <div class="footer-links">
                <div class="link-column">
                    <a href="{{ path('app_home') }}">Accueil</a>
                    <a href="{{ path('app_plan_new') }}">Éditeur</a>
                    <a href="{{ path('app_item_catalog_index') }}">Catalogue</a>
                    <a href="{{ path('app_plan_index') }}">Mes projets</a>
                </div>

                <div class="link-column">
                    <a href="#">À propos de nous</a>
                    <a href="#">Conditions d'utilisation</a>
                    <a href="#">Politique de confidentialité</a>
                    <a href="#">Contactez-nous</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

    </div>
</footer>

</body>
</html>